```

### Required Setup for Clerk Modals

1. Install Dialog component: `npx shadcn@latest add dialog`
2. Install Button component: `npx shadcn@latest add button`
3. Use `routing="virtual"` prop on `<SignIn>` and `<SignUp>` components
4. Wrap Clerk components in shadcn UI `<Dialog>` component
5. Use shadcn UI `<Button>` as the `<DialogTrigger>`

